author: malcolm
msg: Prevent failing tests from obstructing following tests by ensuring that
we always restore the current working directory after a failure.
The majority of this change is simply re-indenting existing code:
(diff_within_renamed_dir, diff_renamed_dir): Use try and finally to
ensure that the current working directory is always restored.
